        -:   38:  * In order to check for equality between two vectors or matrices with floating-point coefficients, it is
        -:   39:  * generally a far better idea to use a fuzzy comparison as provided by isApprox() and
        -:   40:  * isMuchSmallerThan().
        -:   41:  *
